description: This elegant Neckerchief is crafted from high-quality silk, providing a luxurious and soft feel against the skin. Its versatile size and stylish design make it a perfect accessory to elevate any outfit, adding a touch of sophistication and refinement. The Neckerchief's lightweight and flexible fabric allow it to be worn as a chic hair accessory or a classic neck scarf, making it a versatile addition to any fashion-forward wardrobe. Print by Danika Herrick.
